      "content": "it's not just anxiety though. it's like... they're everywhere. every post, every comment, even the people i thought were my friends. it's like the whole world is just one big joke and i'm the punchline. i try to talk to people but they just look at me different now. there's no way to fix this. it's just permanent.",
